{
  "slug": "cwc-makers",
  "name": "Cwc Makers",
  "type": "plugin",
  "description": "Seamless onboarding for the Code-with-Claude Makers Cardputer: one /maker-setup command clones the build-with-claude repo, flashes UIFlow firmware, and installs the Claude Buddy app bundle onto a freshly-plugged-in M5Stack Cardputer-Adv.",
  "longDescription": "One `/maker-setup` command onboards a freshly plugged-in M5Stack Cardputer-Adv: clones the `build-with-claude` repo, flashes UIFlow firmware, and installs the Claude Buddy app bundle. Two bundled skills (`m5-onboard`, `cardputer-buddy`) handle device detection, flashing, and app deployment, so no manual ESP32 tooling is needed.",
